data.description: TWO UNIT HOME - EASY CONVERSION TO ONE FAMILY IF NEEDED! Projected rent would be $1100 for each unit, making this an amazing opportunity for an investor who wants to rent both units or someone that wants to live in one and offset mortgage with the rent received from the other - or use as a single family home and have the benefit of alot of square footage! This property's exterior features include a covered front porch and back patio/yard. Both units of this home feature three finished levels of living space with walk-up attics that are both finished. This home is within walking distance to many locations in Lansford, including: food,shopping and the public track field across the street! This property is close to many different outdoor locations, including: hiking, hunting, and the much loved town of Jim Thorpe! Schedule today!
